<h2>What's New in 1.9.19</h2>  <ul><li><strong>More reliable Claude Code sign-in</strong> — AIQuota now falls back to the web sign-in flow when stored Claude credentials are rejected.</li> <li><strong>Clearer widget gauges</strong> — empty gauge tracks are easier to see while still using system semantic colors.</li> <li><strong>Cleaner widget details</strong> — widgets now match the main app and no longer show a confusing amber `$0.00` spent line.</li> <li><strong>Better macOS 26 readability</strong> — the menu bar popover has stronger contrast when floating over bright windows.</li></ul> <img src="https://github.com/niederme/ai-quota/releases/download/v1.9.19/AIQuota-1.9.19.png" alt="AIQuota 1.9.19" width="600"> 
